import { Fragment } from 'react' const Rules = () => { return (

Rules of Juniper Green game

The game has three rules :

Player 1 choose a number between 1 and 100. In turn, each player choose a number from multiples or divisors of the previously chosen number by his opponents and less than 100.

A number is not played more than once Looser are player who do not find multiples or common divisors
at the previously chosen number .

); } export default Rules;
